Package com.commercetools.graphql.api.types

Class CustomerGroup

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.graphql.api.types.CustomerGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
ReferenceExpandable, Versioned
public class CustomerGroup extends Object implements Versioned, ReferenceExpandable
A customer can be a member in a customer group (e.g. reseller, gold member). A customer group can be used in price calculations with special prices being assigned to certain customer groups.
